      longDescription: "When the whole group decides to get away, Lazy Bear Lodge is built for it. Sleeping six across a queen, a double, and a pull-out sofa, there's space to spread out without stepping on each other. The large living area is the natural gathering point — morning coffee, card games at midnight, everything in between. Outside: a fire pit, a dock, canoes, and the Madawaska rolling past. Pets welcome.",
